Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Sniff, sniff. Sniff, sniff.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{oh cool, no ending this episode}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,I've been thinking all this time about who I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,When Nana passed away, I felt so lonely and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,I started to wonder why I even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,And then I finally remembered.{really?}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,was just a Shadow in that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,One day, a Shadow living in that\N world awakened to human emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,He made himself forget that he was a Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,He wanted people to like him,\N and that's how he came to look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,But Shadows aren't allowed to stay in the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:47.31,Default,,0090,0090,0015,,when you meet Nana in Heaven, please apologize for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,Tell her I'm sorry I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,Teddie,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,Nanako's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,Nana's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:00:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0015,,Nana's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0001,,{\fad(0,800)}Wow! That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who meets all of the criteria must be here in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer must have a connection to both Konishi and Ms. Yamano...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as be in a position to observe our actions periodically to some extent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, it must be someone who could approach your house without arousing suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should review the information with everyone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.57,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm returning to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's something I wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...{'m gay for you}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere deep down,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.64,0:02:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's more like I was jealous of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were like me.{definitely gay}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming from the city to the countryside,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be bored out of your mind here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as soon as you got here, you called your Persona
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and brought us together. You're a real hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm proud of you...{nohomo}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about? {UH OH HE KNOWS}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a problem with how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I... {oh man oh god oh man oh god}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to look you in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to hit me! {what is this, k-on?}{what is this, BRS?}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think out of everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be acknowledged by you the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a good one to knock out all this crap inside of me.{real gay}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want us to be equals, so c'mon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you wanted? {aww shit}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my second time punching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, this doesn't make us equals at all. {（´<_｀　）}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going around in circles on my own again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How humiliating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd be equals if we both hit each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your punches are brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was seeing stars there for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:03:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a lot better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing, {life}partner!
