Dialogue: 2,0:04:12.73,0:04:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's{\i0} the culprit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoto, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something that's been bothering me about him for some time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure how to put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the possibility isn't zero, then we can't rule him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he said he came to escort Ms. Yamano and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine he had contact with Konishi since she found Ms. Yamano's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that fit the criteria too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that just a coincidence?
