Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:04:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with Amagi,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the people who went missing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had been thrown into the TV by Namatame who was disguised as a deliveryman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He came up to their front door and brazenly rang the doorbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But only Kubo Mitsuo testified about what happened when he went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He blacked out in the police interrogation room when he turned himself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He turned himself in? I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My uncle confirmed the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, no one took Kubo's confession seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's when...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kubo was investigated by...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look so angry? {maybe because you killed his cousin idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako's room isn't around here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dojima, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be up. You need your rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adachi, where's Namatame?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namatame's already been relocated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for you so I could tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who authorized that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still more I need to ask him about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those first two murders have been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His motives are shaky,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his alibi is rock solid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this more of your "detective's intuition"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's already been relocated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use hassling me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you kids should really get home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting in the way of police business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to confirm something with Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell us about the time Ms. Yamano went missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporters were forcing their way into the inn,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I went to serve as an undercover bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My memory's kinda hazy that far back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you ever speak with Konishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I did. She discovered the announcer's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she didn't know much about it, so I only talked with her once or twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you learn anything about the warning letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warning letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... I don't really remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I gave it to you to take down to the crime lab for processing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me you forgot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your accident was right after that, and what with one thing and another, it sorta slipped my mind.{>afterwards, what is this, BE?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what're you asking me all this for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get to the station and report in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more thing, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know for certain now that the first two murders weren't Namatame's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adachi, do you have any idea who that might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause we think it mighta been you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuckin' admit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We already know Namatame's the one who put them all in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put them all in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know something about the method behind the murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been fixated on something you once said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I finally understand why.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you recall when I read Namatame's diary at the scene of Dojima's accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the victims who survived and were never released to the public are written here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I note that Mr. Morooka's address is absent from the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Then that settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How, I wonder, would that "settle" anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's odd you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the police had no idea there had been other attempted murders related to the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet when Naoto read the list of names,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you raised no objection.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say to that, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I said I'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear he ran this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit. Where the hell'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teddie, in my dream, you vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Teddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I'm just a Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be something I can do!{the jp is lit. "something only i can do", dunno if you want to change it}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done running away!
