Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,I can't find his exact location.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Darn it, Teddie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Why aren't you here when we need you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Please come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Teddie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Master! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Y-You little... Where the hell were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,You idiot! Bad bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,You're so late! Who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,I'm bear-y sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Where have you been this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,I figured out a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0005,,Stuff about me... and that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? What's the problem with being a Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you now possess the power of Persona.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it follow, then, that you must've developed an ego?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Teddie's practically human, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're the same as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same as humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teddie,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stay with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want you to go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Teddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you! I-I'm so glad I met you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to look for him too! Leave it to Fuzzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, I'm getting something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thattaway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are very persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adachi, are you really the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our world will probably become just like this place soon enough anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, this place will be reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans will turn into Shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't change the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who threw Ms. Yamano into the TV, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! That isn't his real body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real Adachi is somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shopping district?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are somehow different this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like he's gained some strong power after coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say this world has taken a real shine to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like it's given me everything I've ever wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the monsters don't attack me at all.\N Maybe they can tell we have the same goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me, come and get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see which of us this world favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:13:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll handle things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on{senpai} and get Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:24.09,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fax0.5\fscx90\blur0.625\c&H0F3B4F&\b1\frx14\fry18\frz346.3\move(779,89,744,89,26,2362)}Am{\fax0.47}a{\fax0.45}gi {\fax0.5\fs31}Inn
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my inn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.09,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This shithole's been so boring that I spent every day glued to the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had been secretly rooting for this woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but then she...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what'd you call me out here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that talk about you having an affair and whatnot... It's all a lie, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to explain myself to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.91,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't deny it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You caught my eye,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it turns out you're just another worthless bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me call for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, shut up, shut up, shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you need to see what it's like to fear for your life. It'll get your head straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She fell in...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! So people can go completely inside!{that's what she said}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That happened in our lobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned about the Midnight Channel through some rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was pure coincidence that I touched the screen and discovered my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I burst out laughing when I found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew right away this was going to be interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you tested it out on Yamano Mayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all. I'm a very sincere fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just trying to punish the stupid bitch a little for betraying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn in Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagi! Satonaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in fighting back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inaba will disappear into the fog soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will become reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.25,0:16:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teddie, don't lose sight of Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Konishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you call me in for more questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were getting pretty cozy with that Namatame...{I'm working for someone named namatame lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's all cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.69,0:16:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep your little secret if you do as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm not good enough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how to deal with girls like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, high school girls today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world's gone straight to shit.{The world is full of shit.}{TITLE DROP!}{sorry, gotta change it}{hey, fuck your shit}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on your knees and beg, and maybe I'll let you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if I'd walk into a deathtrap like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to be the best of the best, and instead they stick me in the boonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I got this sweet power to make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know it was dangerous inside the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I was trying to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bitches and whores{Mayumi and that high schooler} were just gold digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got exactly what they deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything wrong at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a chump!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.64,0:18:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I just tell you the real me is somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! What a tough bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Shadow's on a completely different level from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This fog is going to drive everyone insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do to Namatame?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He called the police in the middle of the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just after they found that Saki girl's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... That's the pattern to the two deaths so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're seeing a girl in a kimono on that weird program, and you think she'll die too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Namatame, do you seriously expect us to believe something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true! If there's any way the police can protect her...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way the police
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are going to make a move based on a ridiculous story like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does sound interesting, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really wanna save her,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why not do it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, you could shelter her somewhere. Somewhere no one could find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where no one could find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save her yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the people who could've received Namatame's call, it ended up being me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was give him a little push.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more people you guys saved, the more he'd kidnap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both sides had the best of intentions, so the cycle would never end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Because of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going bear-serk!{gotta fit in these bear puns while I still can}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu, leave this to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You threw Kubo into the TV, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... he turned himself in pretty quick, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was back when we didn't even know enough to issue a search warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the other officers decided it was just a prank, so they pawned him off on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think anyone would come forward and take the blame for all the incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we closed the case, Namatame would stop "saving" people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't let that happen, or the game would be over.{I lost the game}{the game. you lost it}{goddamn you guys}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told the others I sent him home but threw him inside the TV instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:21:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty good idea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game would be over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was your reason?{"ok"}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta have some excitement in life, don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then you guys had to get involved and ruin my fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.49,0:21:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, Kubo was arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone acted like he was the true culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't they see how badly he copied the crime scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked out in the end, though, because good ol' Namatame kept saving people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the guy started to develop\N some kinda messiah complex, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'm surprised you made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adachi, why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? No reason, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it because I could, and it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was put people in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the world that really kills them, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world reflects people's thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear... Does that mean the real culprits are everyone on the outside, including you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And aren't you high schoolers?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be studying instead of worrying about this crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Study{party} hard, go to a good college, and marry a cute girl.{sounds like a plan.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why get so worked up over things you can't change?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you've got nothing better to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all a bunch of lonely losers!{ronery roosers}{so badly want to put faggots, but... dame da}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.82,0:22:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the lonely one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act so high and mighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fucking cocky brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We'll catch the true killer ourselves!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh shit, my sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.38,0:22:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your world is devoured,\N everyone'll turn into Shadows.{then the world will be one big happy place}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.93,0:22:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too late.{I prefer turning into tang, though}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:22:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pity the fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brats like you are so damned naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your very existence is pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need annoying fucks like you in the new world.{KISS. KISS. KISS. KISS!!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put an end to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:21.00,Default,,0001,0001,0010,,I thought I could just leave you be, but you're like a plague.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0010,,I'll kill you! Let's find out which of us this world favors!{end here and roll credits?}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}Magatsu Izanagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.40,0:23:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}Izanagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be a good boy and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.50,0:23:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.75,0:24:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reality isn't a game!{more like "reality is a shitty game" amirite?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would a brat like you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.50,0:24:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the two worlds will collide!{oh fuck FFIX all over again}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Persona!
